{"id":368725,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":15}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"山东的民歌","genre":"","count":"78","ytitle":"","mtitle":"挖湾泥","ftitle":"","authors":["郭澄清"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭澄清"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星满天，人满湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月儿弯弯挂树尖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一筐湾泥一筐歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山歌越唱人越欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱得月亮钻进地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱得太阳升上天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱得湾底成了湖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱得湾泥堆成山。"}]}